{"tid":1101304,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人有時都好有支那基因，而且閪到爆","createTime":"2019-04-11T02:59:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T11:36:47.000Z","uid":157321,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"07050628c72ffe9f0c4e9dfd24fb9096b08d15a0","tid":1101304,"uid":157321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T02:59:53.000Z","msg":"成日話支那人閪<br />\n香港人都好有支那基因好撚閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日閪口閪面<br />\n（1）無禮貌又多要求<br />\n大學上堂投訴老師PPT太多版搞到佢地要曬紙印唔環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你可以唔print架其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（2）搭飛機當空姐係狗，叫人擺行李閪口閪面話咩「我入面d水晶梨好貴，你咁大力整爛你賠呀？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你唔想人整爛一係自己搬一係好聲好氣提提人，係都要閪面，真係以為自己俾個雞碎咁多錢真係皇帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（3）朝早搭地鐵，為搶位無撞到都閪面。有次有個臭閪港女排我後面郁一郁都話唔好撞到佢。我大大聲講「屌你老母，你咪撚企咁埋咪撞你唔到」跟手收皮。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（4）去旅行打風天機師唔肯飛，係咁屌鳩地勤，話「我聽日要返工，我點算」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（5）有著數成班餓狗搶屎&mdash;航空公司提供免費酒店住宿，成班驚死爭輸係酒店大堂狂奔。酒店職員係咁安撫佢地話人人有份永不落空<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（6）旅行大大聲周街講廣東話，台北最嚴重，成班廢老廢閪大大聲聲傾計跑來跑去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家仲有無其他例子？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b1ffc9029b7c4e64ad31d15565714537029a89","tid":1101304,"uid":50502,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T03:12:06.000Z","msg":"空姐好多都西面 一睇就知香港人 <br />\n搭地鐵你咪可能又個係咩背囊左右fing撞到人又屌鳩人既香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係有時好有支那基因 而係根本同支那人一樣 <br />\n你地心目中好既香港人其實只係少數既85後90後<br />\n00後全部支那化又on9<br />\n80對上既有錢得黎同支那人一樣自大"},{"pid":"52cd85afb470049b487f1001dc5da9931a151153","tid":1101304,"uid":50502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T03:13:02.000Z","msg":"窮既就同支那大種乞衣一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cdfc154118a4c645503b4f068bf45c4e701069d","tid":1101304,"uid":12498,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52cd85afb470049b487f1001dc5da9931a151153","tid":1101304,"uid":50502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T03:13:02.000Z","msg":"窮既就同支那大種乞衣一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T03:14:11.000Z","msg":"香港人=窮嘅大陸人"},{"pid":"9eb71652a9c618aff046ebb0f2d8c38dd2ef86be","tid":1101304,"uid":157321,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"96b1ffc9029b7c4e64ad31d15565714537029a89","tid":1101304,"uid":50502,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T03:12:06.000Z","msg":"空姐好多都西面 一睇就知香港人 <br />\n搭地鐵你咪可能又個係咩背囊左右fing撞到人又屌鳩人既香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係有時好有支那基因 而係根本同支那人一樣 <br />\n你地心目中好既香港人其實只係少數既85後90後<br />\n00後全部支那化又on9<br />\n80對上既有錢得黎同支那人一樣自大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T03:18:53.000Z","msg":"我個case係佢想打我尖入車廂<br />\n我唔俾佢打尖<br />\n我擋住佢 <br />\n佢嬲起上嚟咪閪鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即屌鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係...00後成班海底撈喜茶<br />\n食撚死佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又玩抖音微信<br />\n俾錢又用支那寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw你講80前個堆又自大又愛國<br />\n00後又閪<br />\n我地呢代8，90後係夾心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa95bf4618b22e95947c6697dcac32b87c54bd00","tid":1101304,"uid":59929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T03:19:16.000Z","msg":"